docs.lead_paragraph: THE royal babies of Callander, the Dionne quintuplets in their glassed-in haven amid high snowdrifts and frost-racked fir trees, will soon be celebrating their second Christmas, with Dr. Allan Roy Dafoe in the role of Santa Claus. On May 28 they will have their second birthday.

headline.main: A VISIT TO THE DIONNES AND THEIR SANTA; Dr. Dafoe, Patron Saint of the Quintuplets, Tells How They Are Being Brought Up

docs.abstract: Feature article on life of the quintuplets
